high_descs: Walk towards and turn left to the dresser.
Pick the credit card from the dresser.
Turn right towards the drawer.
Put the credit card inside the drawer.
Turn left to the fridge.
Pick the credit card from the fridge.
Turn left towards the drawer.
Put the credit card inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To put the  credit card inside the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to reach the side part of the desk on the left side on which microwave oven is placed
Take a credit card from the back side of the oven
Now come to the front side the drawer
Open the drawer and put the credit card inside of it and close the drawer
Turn back and walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge and take a credit card from it and close the door
Turn back and walk towards the drawer again
Open the drawer and put the second credit card inside of it and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card in the drawer

high_descs: Turn left to reach the kitchen and reach the dresser,
Pick up the credit card from the dresser.
Turn left to reach the bottom drawer.
Put the credit card in the bottom drawer.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Pick up the credit card from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the drawer.
Put the credit card in the bottom drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the two credit cards in the bottom drawer.
